Sentencas: An auxiliary power unit (APU) is presented that is fuelled with diesel, thermally self-sustaining, and based on a solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC).
Titulo: Auxiliary power unit based on a solid oxide fuel cell and fuelled with diesel

Sentencas: The APU is rated at I kW electrical, and can generate electrical power after a 3 h warm-up phase.
Titulo: Auxiliary power unit based on a solid oxide fuel cell and fuelled with diesel

Sentencas: System features include a dry catalytic partial oxidation (CPOX) diesel reformer, a 30 cell SOFC stack with an open cathode, and a porous-media afterburner.
Titulo: Auxiliary power unit based on a solid oxide fuel cell and fuelled with diesel

Sentencas: The APU does not require a supply of external water.
Titulo: Auxiliary power unit based on a solid oxide fuel cell and fuelled with diesel

Sentencas: The SOFC stack is an outcome of a development partnership with H.C. Starck GmbH and Fraunhofer IKTS, and is discussed in detail in an accompanying paper.
Titulo: Auxiliary power unit based on a solid oxide fuel cell and fuelled with diesel
